**Step 3** — Click **File** in the top menu. Click **Save As**.

**Step 4** — This is the important part. At the bottom of the Save As window find the dropdown that says **Save as type**. Click it and change it from **Text Documents (\*.txt)** to **All Files (\*.\*)**.

**Step 5** — In the **File name** field at the top delete whatever is there and type exactly:
```
manifest.json
```

**Step 6** — Navigate to your `wisewandr` folder on the Desktop. Make sure you are saving it there.

**Step 7** — Click **Save**.

---

## Confirm It Saved Correctly

Go to your `wisewandr` folder on the Desktop. You should see a file called `manifest.json`. 

If you see `manifest.json.txt` it saved with the wrong extension. Go back to Notepad and repeat Step 4 — make sure you changed Save as type to **All Files** before saving.

If you see `manifest.json` with no `.txt` at the end you did it perfectly. ✅

---

Now you have all four main files ready:
```
✅ index.html
✅ solowandr-home.html
✅ solowandr-final-logo.svg
✅ manifest.json